nodes.text: Patch was a male Human who served as a lieutenant with the Oquan, a bounty hunter group that operated on the planet of Naalol. During the time of the Galactic Civil War, the Rebel Alliance procurement officer Lieutenant Talnar crash-landed on Naalol and the Oquan planned to capture him, so that they could sell him to the Galactic Empire. Patch and the Oquan lieutenant Selana subsequently led a group of fifteen Oquan who subdued Talnar and took him captive.
